#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[0].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.caption"
msgid "New Zone Wizard"
msgstr "新建区域向导"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[3].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label1.caption"
msgid "Welcome to the New Zone Wizard"
msgstr "欢迎使用新建区域向导"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[15].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label10.caption"
msgid ""
"Create a copy of a zone containing inly Name Server (NS), Start of Authority "
"(SOA), and possibly glue Host (A) records. A server containing a stub zone "
"is not authoritative for that zone."
msgstr "创建一个仅包含名称服务器 (NS)、起始授权机构 (SOA)，以及可能的粘附主机 (A) 记录的区域副本。包含存根区域的服务器并不是该区域的权威服务器。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[16].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label11.caption"
msgid ""
"Store the zone in Active Directory (available only if DNS server is a "
"writeable domain controller)"
msgstr "将区域存储在 Active Directory 中（仅当 DNS 服务器是可写域控制器时可用）"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[17].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label12.caption"
msgid "Active Directory Zone Replication Scope"
msgstr "Active Directory 区域复制范围"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[18].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label13.caption"
msgid ""
"You can select how you want DNS data replicated throughout your network."
msgstr "你可以选择 DNS 数据在整个网络中的复制方式。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[19].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label14.caption"
msgid "Select how you want zone data replicated:"
msgstr "选择区域数据的复制方式："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[20].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label15.caption"
msgid "To all DNS servers running on domain controllers in this forest:"
msgstr "到此林中域控制器上运行的所有 DNS 服务器："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[21].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label16.caption"
msgid "To all DNS servers running on domain controllers in this domain:"
msgstr "到此域中域控制器上运行的所有 DNS 服务器："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[22].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label17.caption"
msgid ""
"To all domain controllers in this domain (for Windows 2000 compatibility):"
msgstr "复制到此域中的所有域控制器（用于 Windows 2000 兼容性）："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[23].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label18.caption"
msgid ""
"To all domain controllers specified in the scoper of this directory "
"partition:"
msgstr "到此目录分区范围中指定的所有域控制器："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[24].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label19.caption"
msgid "Zone Name"
msgstr "区域名称"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[4].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label2.caption"
msgid "This wizard helps you create a new zone for your DNS server."
msgstr "此向导帮助你为 DNS 服务器创建新区。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[25].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label20.caption"
msgid "What is the name of the new zone?"
msgstr "新区的名称是什么？"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[26].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label21.caption"
msgid ""
"The zone name specifies the portion of the DNS namespace for which this "
"server is autoritative. It might be your organization's domain name (for "
"example, example.com) or a portion of the domain name (for example, newzone."
"example.com). The zone name is not the name of the DNS server."
msgstr "区域名称指定 DNS 命名空间中由该服务器负责的部分。它可以是组织的域名（例如 example.com），也可以是域名的一部分（例如 newzone.example.com）。区域名称不是 DNS 服务器的名称。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[27].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label22.caption"
msgid "Zone name:"
msgstr "Zone name："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[28].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label23.caption"
msgid "Zone File"
msgstr "区域文件"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[29].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label24.caption"
msgid ""
"You can create a new zone file or use a file copied from another DNS server."
msgstr "你可以创建新的区域文件，或使用从另一台 DNS 服务器复制的文件。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[30].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label25.caption"
msgid ""
"Do you want to create a new zone file or use an existing file that you have "
"copied from another DNS server?"
msgstr "要创建新的区域文件，还是使用已从另一台 DNS 服务器复制的现有文件？"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[31].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label26.caption"
msgid ""
"To use this existing file, ensure that it has been copied to the folder "
"%SystemRoot%\\system32\\dns on this server, and then click Next."
msgstr "要使用现有文件，请确保它已复制到此服务器的 %SystemRoot%\\system32\\dns 文件夹，然后单击“下一步”。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[32].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label27.caption"
msgid "Create a new file with this file name:"
msgstr "使用此文件名创建新文件："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[33].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label28.caption"
msgid "Use this existing file:"
msgstr "Use this existing file："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[34].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label29.caption"
msgid ""
"You can specify that this DNS zone accepts secure, nonsecure, or no dynamic "
"updates."
msgstr "你可以指定此 DNS 区域接受安全动态更新、非安全动态更新，或不接受动态更新。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[5].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label3.caption"
msgid ""
"A zone translates DNS names to related data, such as IP addresses or network "
"services."
msgstr "区域将 DNS 名称转换为相关数据，例如 IP 地址或网络服务。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[35].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label30.caption"
msgid "Dynamic Update"
msgstr "动态更新"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[36].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label31.caption"
msgid ""
"Dynamic updates enable DNS client computers to register and dynamically "
"update their resource records with a DNS server whenever changes occur."
msgstr "动态更新允许 DNS 客户端计算机在发生更改时向 DNS 服务器注册并动态更新其资源记录。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[37].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label32.caption"
msgid "Select the type of dynamic updates you want to allow:"
msgstr "选择允许的动态更新类型："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[38].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label33.caption"
msgid "Allow only secure dynamic updates (recommanded for Active Directory)"
msgstr "仅允许安全动态更新（推荐用于 Active Directory）"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[39].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label34.caption"
msgid "This option is available only for Active Directory-integrated zones."
msgstr "此选项仅适用于 Active Directory 集成区域。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[40].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label35.caption"
msgid "Allow both nonsecure and secure dynamic updates"
msgstr "同时允许非安全和安全的动态更新"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[41].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label36.caption"
msgid "Dynamic updates of resource records are accepted from any client."
msgstr "接受来自任何客户端的资源记录动态更新。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[42].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label37.caption"
msgid ""
"This option is a significant security vulnerability because updates can be "
"accepted from untrusted sources."
msgstr "此选项存在重大安全风险，因为它会接受来自不受信任来源的更新。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[43].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label38.caption"
msgid "Do not allow dynamic updates"
msgstr "不允许动态更新"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[44].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label39.caption"
msgid ""
"Dynamic updates of resource records are not accepted by this zone. You must "
"update these records manually."
msgstr "此区域不接受资源记录的动态更新。必须手动更新这些记录。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[6].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label4.caption"
msgid "To continue, click Next."
msgstr "创建一个仅包含名称服务器 (NS)、起始授权机构 (SOA)，以及可能的粘附主机 (A) 记录的区域副本。包含存根区域的服务器并不是该区域的权威服务器。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[45].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label40.caption"
msgid "Completing the New Zone Wizard"
msgstr "正在完成新建区域向导"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[46].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label41.caption"
msgid ""
"You have successfully completed the New Zone Wizard. You specified the "
"following settings:"
msgstr "你已成功完成新建区域向导。你指定了以下设置："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[47].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label42.caption"
msgid ""
"Note: You should now add records to the zone or ensure that records are "
"updated dynamically. You can then verify name resolution using nslookup."
msgstr "注意：现在应向区域添加记录，或确保记录可动态更新。然后可以使用 nslookup 验证名称解析。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[48].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label43.caption"
msgid "To close this wizard and create the new zone, click Finish."
msgstr "要关闭此向导并创建新区，请点击“完成”。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[7].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label5.caption"
msgid "Zone Type"
msgstr "区域类型"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[8].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label6.caption"
msgid "The DNS server supports various types of zones and storage."
msgstr "DNS 服务器支持多种区域类型和存储方式。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[9].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label7.caption"
msgid "Select the type of zone you want to create:"
msgstr "选择要创建的区域类型："

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[13].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label8.caption"
msgid "Creates a copy of a zone that can be updated directly on this server."
msgstr "创建可直接在此服务器上更新的区域副本。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[14].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.label9.caption"
msgid ""
"Create a copy of a zone that exists on another server. This option helps "
"balance the processing load of primary servers and provides fault tolerance."
msgstr "创建另一个服务器上现有区域的副本。此选项有助于平衡主服务器的处理负载并提供容错能力。"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[10].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.radiobutton1.caption"
msgid "Primary zone"
msgstr "主要区域"

#: uvisnewzonewizard.lrj:$.strings.[11].value
msgctxt "tvisnewzonewizard.radiobutton2.caption"
